  <!-- Introducción de la actividad -->  
  <paragraphs>
    <title><custom ref="narrative-actividad-titulo"/></title>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>The purpose of this How Many Do You See is for students to subitize or use grouping strategies to describe the images they see. Recognizing and describing one more than a given quantity will be useful in the next section when students work on creating and identifying one more than a given quantity or number.</p>
<p>When students use the structure of the 5-frame to recognize and describe quantities, they look for and make use of structure (MP7).</p>
